title: Hour 2 - Lakers Start 0-4, Cooper Manning
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Lakers Start 0-4, Cooper Manning
description:
Dan addresses the Los Angeles Lakers 0-4 start to this NBA season. And he talks to Cooper Manning about being a son, brother and father to famous quarterbacks (Archie, Peyton, Eli, and Arch Manning).
